# CODEOWNERS - Team Ownership for Monorepo

# Development Team owns apps and packages
/apps/                    @dev-team
/packages/                @dev-team

# QA Team owns features (test scenarios)
/features/                @qa-team

# Business Analyst Team owns requirements and user stories
/docs/requirements/       @ba-team
/docs/user-stories/       @ba-team

# BA + DEV collaborate on specs
/docs/specs/              @ba-team @dev-team

# Scrum Master/All teams own sprint notes
/docs/sprint-notes/       @scrum-master

# GitHub workflows
/.github/workflows/       @dev-team

# Cursor rules
/.cursor/                 @dev-team

# Note: Replace @dev-team, @qa-team, @ba-team, @scrum-master with actual GitHub usernames or teams
# Example: /apps/ @john-doe @jane-smith

